de Cindy Bradley.

139
00:11:34,507 --> 00:11:36,475
Pero eso no es de Cindy.

140
00:11:36,576 --> 00:11:42,537
Es de William Lewis, bajo el asiento,
de Hollywood.

141
00:11:46,886 --> 00:11:50,845
